{
  "design_notes": "The chart is designed as an accessible 'Easy' difficulty to match the 155 BPM pulse of the song. Note densities strictly correlate to the energy curve, scaling from a driving 3-note-per-bar intro to a calmer drop, and building to a peak 5-note-per-bar sequence with downbeat accents during the peak energy drop in section S2. Gaps in the raw onset data have been carefully populated using grid positions to prevent any awkward pauses, keeping the flow continuous and comfortable. Holds are strategically placed on sustained musical events to represent about 15% of the notes.",
